Games vs. Other Media


Importance of the player is paramount. This motivation 
distinguishes games. At every step of the game, the player 
is involved, whether  consciously or not. 
-Design – Player agency as driving factor 
-Story – Player dictates as much as writer 
-Success – Players choose to buy or not (Steam) 
-Game itself – by definition, player’s motivations for 
playing determine if the game is actually a game 

